{"tha-ap67:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap67:0.2":"Sakacintaniyavagga ","tha-ap67:0.3":"Bhisadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap67:1.1":"“Vessabhu nama namena, ","tha-ap67:1.2":"isinam tatiyo ahu; ","tha-ap67:1.3":"Kananam vanamogayha, ","tha-ap67:1.4":"vihasi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap67:2.1":"Bhisamulalam ganhitva, ","tha-ap67:2.2":"agamam buddhasantikam; ","tha-ap67:2.3":"Tanca buddhassa padasim, ","tha-ap67:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap67:3.1":"Karena ca paramattho, ","tha-ap67:3.2":"vessabhuvarabuddhina; ","tha-ap67:3.3":"Sukhaham nabhijanami, ","tha-ap67:3.4":"samam tena kutottarim. ","tha-ap67:4.1":"Carimo vattate mayham, ","tha-ap67:4.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap67:4.3":"Hatthinagena santena, ","tha-ap67:4.4":"kusalam ropitam maya. ","tha-ap67:5.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap67:5.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap67:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap67:5.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap67:6.1":"Samodhana ca rajano, ","tha-ap67:6.2":"solasa manujadhipa; ","tha-ap67:6.3":"Kappamhi cuddase asum, ","tha-ap67:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap67:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap67:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap67:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap67:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhisadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap67:9.1":"Bhisadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}